  "prompt": "What is the omen behind itchy palms?",
  "response": "The belief that itchy palms have a specific omen is rooted in various cultural superstitions. Many traditions assign different meanings to the sensation of an itchy palm, and interpretations can vary:\n\n1. **Itchy Right Palm**: In some cultures, an itchy right palm is thought to signify that you will receive money or unexpected financial gain.\n\n2. **Itchy Left Palm**: Conversely, an itchy left palm is often associated with the idea of losing money or experiencing a financial setback.\n\nThese interpretations are largely anecdotal and rooted in folklore rather than scientific fact. Different cultures and regions may have their own unique beliefs and interpretations regarding itchy palms. It's important to note that if you experience persistent itching, it might be best to consult a healthcare professional to rule out any medical issues.",
